title: RIP Jan-Michael Vincent (w/ Mike Finoia, Shuli Egar, Joe DeRosa)
description: Jay and Christine accidentally go to a lice party over the weekend. After a run in in the Sirius XM elevator, the gang finds out the incredible Gary Clark Jr. is a Camper. Jacob gives a heart felt eulogy at the Jan-Michael Vincent Memorial and Joe DeRosa shares a strange sex story on at the live show on the Impractical Joker's Cruise.
author: podcasts@siriusxm.com (Comedy Central)
